---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <div class="text-sm font-light">
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Oscar, a software developer turned entrepreneur from Belgium.
        I'm the founder of Softwhale, a digital agency that helps startups build
        and ship amazing products.
        <br />
        What products do we build ?
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Mobile Apps</li>
        <li>Web Apps</li>
        <li>Websites</li>
        <li>Back-end</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Beyond coding, I'm passionate about design, illustration, animation and 3D
      modelling and traveling. An unusual hobby of mine is collecting vintage
      passports, they're interesting pieces of history to me.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
